1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:42,229
[I Don't Want to Be Friends With You]

3
00:02:24,610 --> 00:02:26,500
[Application Form for Regular Institutions
of Higher Learning - Li Qing Tong]

4
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:38,420
[Lin Yang Teachers College]

5
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:53,340
[Li Qing Tong - Lin Yang Teachers College]

6
00:02:56,190 --> 00:03:02,520
[Episode 16]
[People Who Have Met Will Meet Again]

7
00:03:03,430 --> 00:03:04,310
Let me put it on for you.

8
00:03:06,870 --> 00:03:07,750
Hua.

9
00:03:08,990 --> 00:03:11,870
What I said before
wasn't because I was drunk.

10
00:03:12,590 --> 00:03:13,470
What was that?

11
00:03:14,470 --> 00:03:15,390
I like you.

12
00:03:17,870 --> 00:03:18,790
No matter where you are,

13
00:03:19,670 --> 00:03:20,910
you can't be in a relationship
with anyone else

14
00:03:21,270 --> 00:03:22,230
but me.

15
00:03:23,190 --> 00:03:24,590
We'll be together sooner or later.

16
00:03:25,710 --> 00:03:26,870
We must be together.

17
00:03:29,230 --> 00:03:30,110
What if...

18
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:31,710
I leave?

19
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:33,270
Then I'll find you.

20
00:03:34,510 --> 00:03:35,470
No matter where you are,

21
00:03:35,950 --> 00:03:37,150
I will find you.

22
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:40,030
I have to go now.

23
00:03:58,670 --> 00:03:59,550
Young girl,

24
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:02,070
remember to call me when you arrive.

25
00:04:02,150 --> 00:04:04,740
Remember to tell us your dormitory number
as soon as possible.

26
00:04:04,830 --> 00:04:05,720
Did you hear it?

27
00:04:05,850 --> 00:04:08,420
I know. You've said it a million times.

28
00:04:09,390 --> 00:04:11,500
Remember to take care of your money.

29
00:04:11,710 --> 00:04:14,470
That's thousands of dollars.
Be careful, don't let it be stolen.

30
00:04:14,950 --> 00:04:16,339
I wouldn't even go to the bathroom.

31
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:18,140
I just put it in my pocket.

32
00:04:18,230 --> 00:04:19,990
Of course you can go to the bathroom.

33
00:04:20,070 --> 00:04:21,060
Don't suppress yourself.

34
00:04:21,149 --> 00:04:22,810
Remember not to carry your bag
on your back,

35
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:23,780
Carry it on your front.

36
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:26,180
Put the change in your pockets
and take it out whenever you need it.

37
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:27,150
Did you hear that?

38
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:30,230
Oh, by the way,

39
00:04:30,310 --> 00:04:32,380
if anyone asks you
what you're going to do,

40
00:04:32,470 --> 00:04:33,750
don't say you're going to school.

41
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,630
Say you're going to visit your relatives.

42
00:04:35,820 --> 00:04:37,030
You need to disguise yourself.

43
00:04:37,790 --> 00:04:38,670
It works.

44
00:04:48,140 --> 00:04:49,020
You see...

45
00:04:49,330 --> 00:04:51,130
It's good for our daughter
to go to college.

46
00:04:51,210 --> 00:04:52,780
Why are you crying?

47
00:04:55,110 --> 00:04:56,500
Don't cry.

48
00:04:58,950 --> 00:05:00,210
Go and comfort your mother.

49
00:05:00,330 --> 00:05:02,000
-No.
-Mum.

50
00:05:02,470 --> 00:05:05,870
I will come back during the holidays.

51
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:08,200
Why are you crying?

52
00:05:08,300 --> 00:05:09,750
Yes. You see...

53
00:05:11,790 --> 00:05:12,830
Don't you always say

54
00:05:13,340 --> 00:05:15,100
you're tired of me at home?

55
00:05:18,910 --> 00:05:19,790
But,

56
00:05:20,190 --> 00:05:22,710
It's better to be annoyed
than not seeing you.

57
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:27,190
I prefer to be annoyed
rather than not see you.

58
00:05:29,230 --> 00:05:30,990
I really owe you this life.

59
00:05:31,590 --> 00:05:33,180
I raised you with a lot of effort.

60
00:05:33,270 --> 00:05:34,150
You...

61
00:05:34,230 --> 00:05:35,830
You're leaving as you said you would.

62
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:44,020
Don't cry, please, don't cry.

63
00:05:44,230 --> 00:05:46,590
Did you deliberately make her cry?

64
00:05:47,110 --> 00:05:48,140
Never mind, girl.

65
00:05:48,230 --> 00:05:49,550
I don't cry.

66
00:05:50,810 --> 00:05:52,340
Don't cry, please.

67
00:05:52,430 --> 00:05:54,950
I'm afraid
you can't take care of yourself.

68
00:05:56,110 --> 00:05:58,070
You are so careless.

69
00:06:01,350 --> 00:06:02,230
Mrs Peony.

70
00:06:02,550 --> 00:06:03,620
I'm leaving too.

71
00:06:04,030 --> 00:06:05,270
Please go to Mohe County
and stay with Lao Duan.

72
00:06:05,790 --> 00:06:06,700
Duan Xiao.

73
00:06:07,270 --> 00:06:09,710
I'll give you the instructions
on behalf of Lao Duan.

74
00:06:10,310 --> 00:06:11,830
Please spread your little wings

75
00:06:12,420 --> 00:06:14,950
and soar where you belong.

76
00:06:17,150 --> 00:06:18,030
Copy that.

77
00:06:24,030 --> 00:06:24,910
Mum.

78
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:26,190
I'm leaving.

79
00:06:26,830 --> 00:06:27,870
Take care of yourself.

80
00:06:31,030 --> 00:06:31,910
Come on,

81
00:06:32,110 --> 00:06:33,230
or you'll miss the train.

82
00:06:34,310 --> 00:06:35,190
Take your bag.

83
00:06:35,510 --> 00:06:36,390
Okay.

84
00:06:37,620 --> 00:06:38,500
I'm leaving.

85
00:06:51,909 --> 00:06:53,850
Remember to keep your money
out of other people's sight.

86
00:06:56,390 --> 00:06:57,830
Girl, remember that,

87
00:06:58,190 --> 00:06:59,100
disguise,

88
00:06:59,180 --> 00:07:00,380
you must learn to disguise.

89
00:07:00,470 --> 00:07:01,710
Go back, go back.

90
00:07:02,390 --> 00:07:04,460
[I've never experienced a parting
like this.]

91
00:07:04,950 --> 00:07:06,910
[Li Qing Tong and I
have never been apart.]

92
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:08,860
Remember to take care of yourself.

93
00:07:09,190 --> 00:07:10,750
-Hurry up. Hurry up.
-Go back, go back.

94
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:12,220
Bye, Auntie. Bye, Uncle.

95
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:13,190
Bye-bye.

96
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:17,830
[But...]

97
00:07:18,030 --> 00:07:20,190
[There's going to be a day
when we'll have to part like this.]

98
00:07:20,710 --> 00:07:22,910
[I might leave her
to go somewhere else too.]

99
00:07:23,390 --> 00:07:24,310
[Go to school,]

100
00:07:24,590 --> 00:07:25,470
[go to work,]

101
00:07:25,590 --> 00:07:26,670
[have my own life.]

102
00:07:27,590 --> 00:07:29,990
[I used to look forward to it,]

103
00:07:31,350 --> 00:07:32,740
[but now]

104
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:33,990
[I'm terrified.]

105
00:07:34,430 --> 00:07:35,710
[Is this]

106
00:07:35,950 --> 00:07:37,510
[what they call "giving up"?]

107
00:07:38,510 --> 00:07:40,350
Don't cry.

108
00:07:58,670 --> 00:08:00,590
This is your student registration form,

109
00:08:00,790 --> 00:08:02,470
and your dormitory key.

110
00:08:02,700 --> 00:08:03,250
[Students Registration Form]

111
00:08:03,510 --> 00:08:04,490
Thank you, teacher.

112
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:05,750
I'm not a teacher.

113
00:08:06,070 --> 00:08:06,950
I'm a student, too.

114
00:08:07,110 --> 00:08:07,990
I'm a sophomore.

115
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:09,630
Buddy,

116
00:08:09,990 --> 00:08:12,350
can't the two of us be in the same dorm?

117
00:08:13,110 --> 00:08:15,030
It's all arranged by the school.

118
00:08:15,950 --> 00:08:16,830
But,

119
00:08:17,790 --> 00:08:19,990
we have a special reason.

120
00:08:23,230 --> 00:08:24,340
She is sick.

121
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:26,830
What's wrong?

122
00:08:28,550 --> 00:08:29,830
She has problems here.

123
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:32,549
She didn't do well
in the college entrance examination,

124
00:08:32,990 --> 00:08:34,940
which left a little psychological shadow.

125
00:08:35,030 --> 00:08:37,230
She can communicate normally
only with me now,

126
00:08:37,309 --> 00:08:38,630
she doesn't talk to anyone else.

127
00:08:39,110 --> 00:08:40,140
I'm afraid that

128
00:08:40,230 --> 00:08:42,870
she won't get along well
with other people in their dorms.

129
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,870
You know?

130
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:49,670
You made up such a lie

131
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:51,470
just to live together?

132
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:57,060
It's not a lie.

133
00:08:57,150 --> 00:09:00,350
Well, If you don't believe us, forget it.

134
00:09:00,830 --> 00:09:03,940
I just wanted to be there for her
through college,

135
00:09:04,030 --> 00:09:05,510
to help her get over it,

136
00:09:05,590 --> 00:09:07,500
to make her feel better.

137
00:09:07,580 --> 00:09:09,470
It's the only thing I can do.

138
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:10,910
Fine.

139
00:09:10,990 --> 00:09:12,110
Let me see.

140
00:09:19,110 --> 00:09:20,780
Then I'll put you two in the same dorm.

141
00:09:25,590 --> 00:09:26,470
Here's your key.

142
00:09:26,790 --> 00:09:27,790
Thanks.

143
00:09:28,430 --> 00:09:29,350
You can go back now.

144
00:09:29,700 --> 00:09:31,220
Thanks. We're leaving now.

145
00:09:31,310 --> 00:09:32,190
See you.

146
00:09:42,190 --> 00:09:44,060
You're nuts. Your whole family are nuts.

147
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:45,260
My whole family?

148
00:09:45,350 --> 00:09:46,750
That's still you.

149
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:49,800
[No. 1 Students' Dormitory]

150
00:09:56,190 --> 00:09:57,860
Are you in this dorm too?

151
00:09:59,030 --> 00:10:00,710
My name is Zhang Wan Man.
What are your names?

152
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:02,020
My name is Li Qing Tong.

153
00:10:02,110 --> 00:10:03,110
My name is Li Jin Bu.

154
00:10:03,350 --> 00:10:03,860
Does...

155
00:10:03,950 --> 00:10:05,870
Does that mean "progress"?

156
00:10:07,230 --> 00:10:08,110
It's very aspiring.

157
00:10:09,150 --> 00:10:10,030
Xiao Shui.

158
00:10:11,470 --> 00:10:13,310
Hello, I'm He Xiao Shui.

159
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:14,910
Li Jin Bu.

160
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:17,630
Li Qing Tong.

161
00:10:17,780 --> 00:10:19,190
-Yeah.
-Hello.

162
00:10:19,350 --> 00:10:21,060
What are you doing with that book?

163
00:10:21,150 --> 00:10:22,790
I've just been to the library.

164
00:10:23,230 --> 00:10:24,660
Going to the library before school starts?

165
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:26,270
The library is not full now.

166
00:10:28,390 --> 00:10:30,350
Well, you guys talk.
I'll do something else.

167
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:36,110
Do you want the upper bed
or the lower one?

168
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:37,750
-Both are fine for me.
-You choose first.

169
00:10:38,430 --> 00:10:39,550
Then I'll take the lower bunk.

170
00:10:46,350 --> 00:10:48,180
You two seem to know each other
from before.

171
00:10:48,270 --> 00:10:50,380
Yes, we are childhood friends.

172
00:10:50,470 --> 00:10:52,030
I really envy you.

173
00:10:52,350 --> 00:10:54,110
Unlike me,

174
00:10:54,190 --> 00:10:55,510
I was alone with no company.

175
00:10:58,230 --> 00:11:00,230
These are squid slices, a
specialty of my hometown. Try.

176
00:11:00,330 --> 00:11:02,010
Eat less, it's fishy.

177
00:11:02,430 --> 00:11:03,710
That's because you haven't tried.

178
00:11:04,630 --> 00:11:05,790
You're in Journalism too?

179
00:11:06,980 --> 00:11:07,860
Yes.

180
00:11:08,710 --> 00:11:09,870
I have inquired.

181
00:11:10,260 --> 00:11:12,710
There are many handsome boys
in our journalism department this year.

182
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:14,740
We can get in touch with them
when the time comes.

183
00:11:14,830 --> 00:11:17,270
[Zhang Wan Man, Zhang Wan Man.]

184
00:11:17,910 --> 00:11:19,910
Anyway, I'm going out for a second.

185
00:11:21,070 --> 00:11:22,140
Where is she going?

186
00:11:22,230 --> 00:11:23,390
On a date.

187
00:11:25,190 --> 00:11:27,260
She is already dating someone?

188
00:11:27,350 --> 00:11:28,780
Didn't she come all alone?

189
00:11:28,870 --> 00:11:30,700
The boy is about 1.85m. He is very tall.

190
00:11:30,790 --> 00:11:31,670
Really?

191
00:11:33,030 --> 00:11:35,310
You two are so gossipy.

192
00:11:35,830 --> 00:11:36,710
Let me see.

193
00:11:38,620 --> 00:11:40,240
[No. 1 Students' Dormitory]

194
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,160
Auntie,

195
00:11:41,230 --> 00:11:42,700
Let me in, please.

196
00:11:42,790 --> 00:11:44,100
No way.

197
00:11:44,190 --> 00:11:46,710
Auntie, I had a fight with my girlfriend,

198
00:11:46,790 --> 00:11:48,550
so I need to make amends with an apology.

199
00:11:49,230 --> 00:11:51,550
You should come during the day.

200
00:11:51,630 --> 00:11:53,380
What are you doing here at night?

201
00:11:53,470 --> 00:11:54,900
I'll have military training tomorrow.

202
00:11:54,990 --> 00:11:56,540
I won't see her for more than ten days.

203
00:11:56,630 --> 00:11:57,860
What if we break up

204
00:11:57,950 --> 00:11:59,580
without seeing her for so many days?

205
00:11:59,660 --> 00:12:01,270
Get a new one.

206
00:12:05,190 --> 00:12:06,970
Auntie, let's do this.

207
00:12:07,060 --> 00:12:08,830
Why don't you give me their dorm number?

208
00:12:09,630 --> 00:12:11,350
You don't even know her phone number.

209
00:12:11,670 --> 00:12:13,030
Is she your girlfriend?

210
00:12:13,550 --> 00:12:14,950
Are you lying?

211
00:12:15,940 --> 00:12:17,030
Security Department,

212
00:12:17,390 --> 00:12:18,740
there's a crook here
in the girls' dormitory.

213
00:12:18,830 --> 00:12:19,780
There's a crook.

214
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:21,360
Hurry up, hurry up.

215
00:12:29,430 --> 00:12:31,230
Is everyone here?

216
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:36,830
I'm very happy when I get to see
young and energetic people like you.

217
00:12:40,830 --> 00:12:42,390
Why is an old lady again?

218
00:12:43,270 --> 00:12:44,990
She isn't the next Yang Ai Ling, is she?

219
00:12:47,350 --> 00:12:48,230
My name is

220
00:12:48,590 --> 00:12:50,070
Ye Mei Xian.

221
00:12:50,820 --> 00:12:52,310
I'm your counsellor.

222
00:12:52,990 --> 00:12:56,540
We are going to spend together
the next three years.

223
00:12:57,350 --> 00:12:59,270
I hope you won't dislike me.

224
00:12:59,710 --> 00:13:01,580
If you have a little problem,

225
00:13:01,670 --> 00:13:03,020
I can put up with it.

226
00:13:03,110 --> 00:13:05,030
If you have any bothering,

227
00:13:05,340 --> 00:13:06,700
I can also help you

228
00:13:06,790 --> 00:13:08,110
by giving you some guidance.

229
00:13:08,190 --> 00:13:09,070
Teacher.

230
00:13:09,190 --> 00:13:11,620
Our biggest worry is that
we won't be able to find a boyfriend.

231
00:13:13,030 --> 00:13:15,020
Look at how promising you are.

232
00:13:15,110 --> 00:13:18,390
Looking for a boyfriend
only two days after school has started.

233
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:20,820
You're here to study,

234
00:13:20,910 --> 00:13:22,510
not to date.

235
00:13:22,750 --> 00:13:25,350
College life is colourful,

236
00:13:25,700 --> 00:13:26,830
but studies

237
00:13:26,910 --> 00:13:28,340
must come first.

238
00:13:29,390 --> 00:13:30,310
Let's get down to business.

239
00:13:30,870 --> 00:13:33,550
Let's talk about the military training.

240
00:13:37,140 --> 00:13:38,270
The 15-day military training,

241
00:13:38,630 --> 00:13:40,310
from training to daily life,

242
00:13:40,590 --> 00:13:43,070
must be conducted in strict accordance
with the standards of military management.

243
00:13:43,430 --> 00:13:44,700
It doesn't matter

244
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:45,790
whether you're a boy or a girl.

245
00:13:46,110 --> 00:13:47,420
The drillmaster is so handsome.

246
00:13:47,510 --> 00:13:48,420
Get up at six o'clock.

247
00:13:48,510 --> 00:13:50,500
Run to the playground in three minutes.
Hold your own.

248
00:13:50,590 --> 00:13:51,470
No days off.

249
00:13:51,550 --> 00:13:52,430
No delays.

250
00:13:52,590 --> 00:13:53,510
No early leave.

251
00:13:53,640 --> 00:13:54,930
Those who can't stand it

252
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,350
are all useless here.

253
00:13:56,620 --> 00:13:58,510
Don't even think about pretending
to be sick or fainting.

254
00:13:58,790 --> 00:14:00,750
Anyone who dares to be lazy
will get harsh punishment.

255
00:14:00,870 --> 00:14:02,630
-Understood?
-Yes, sir!

256
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:03,790
Attention!

257
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:05,550
Dress to the right!

258
00:14:05,990 --> 00:14:06,870
Eyes front!

259
00:14:07,590 --> 00:14:08,700
Goose step kicking practice.

260
00:14:08,790 --> 00:14:09,670
One.

261
00:14:12,590 --> 00:14:13,470
Two.

262
00:14:13,990 --> 00:14:14,870
One.

263
00:14:15,350 --> 00:14:18,580
♫ Unity is strength ♫

264
00:14:18,670 --> 00:14:20,100
♫ This strength is iron ♫

265
00:14:20,190 --> 00:14:21,900
♫ This strength is steel ♫

266
00:14:21,990 --> 00:14:25,220
♫ Stronger than iron
stronger than steel ♫

267
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:31,970
Go! Go! Go!

268
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:32,910
Fast up! Fast up!

269
00:14:33,750 --> 00:14:34,630
Hurry up!

270
00:14:34,750 --> 00:14:35,630
My shoes.

271
00:14:36,190 --> 00:14:37,070
My cap.

272
00:14:38,190 --> 00:14:40,100
I can't run any further.

273
00:14:58,590 --> 00:14:59,470
What would you like to have?

274
00:15:01,550 --> 00:15:02,950
A little of all four, please.

275
00:15:05,110 --> 00:15:06,590
You can only choose one.

276
00:15:07,950 --> 00:15:08,830
Why is that?

277
00:15:10,070 --> 00:15:11,790
It's easy to choose a dish,

278
00:15:12,230 --> 00:15:14,230
but it's hard to choose
how to live a life.

279
00:15:15,470 --> 00:15:17,550
We all need to know where we come from

280
00:15:18,070 --> 00:15:19,230
and where we are going back to.

281
00:15:19,790 --> 00:15:21,070
You need to learn

282
00:15:21,630 --> 00:15:23,430
to give up many things.

283
00:15:24,310 --> 00:15:26,780
[We all need to know where we came from]

284
00:15:26,870 --> 00:15:29,350
[and where we are going back to.]

285
00:15:49,310 --> 00:15:50,310
Maybe,

286
00:15:51,350 --> 00:15:53,310
we should call our daughter again?

287
00:15:54,110 --> 00:15:55,790
You just called yesterday.

288
00:15:57,270 --> 00:15:58,990
She's in military training.

289
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,360
It's so tiring.

290
00:16:00,450 --> 00:16:01,340
What if she can't eat or drink well?

291
00:16:01,430 --> 00:16:02,950
What if she gets sick?

292
00:16:10,590 --> 00:16:11,470
Hello?

293
00:16:12,990 --> 00:16:13,870
Girl.

294
00:16:15,190 --> 00:16:16,750
I was just thinking of calling you.

295
00:16:21,150 --> 00:16:22,550
Your mum is cracking sunflower seeds.

296
00:16:22,830 --> 00:16:24,470
You know that I miss you.

297
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:28,030
Are you going to eat? Okay, okay.

298
00:16:28,110 --> 00:16:29,150
Go ahead, go ahead.

299
00:16:29,590 --> 00:16:30,380
Eat more.

300
00:16:30,460 --> 00:16:31,380
Tell me if you run out of money,

301
00:16:31,470 --> 00:16:32,350
I'll send you money.

302
00:16:32,710 --> 00:16:33,710
Okay, okay, go ahead.

303
00:16:42,790 --> 00:16:43,670
Oh.

304
00:16:44,070 --> 00:16:46,630
I... I forgot to ask you to talk to her.

305
00:16:47,150 --> 00:16:48,540
It doesn't matter if I say it or not.

306
00:16:48,630 --> 00:16:49,740
You're the father,

307
00:16:49,830 --> 00:16:50,830
I'm the stepmother.

308
00:16:51,630 --> 00:16:53,590
Why did you get into a mood?

309
00:16:54,070 --> 00:16:55,110
Get into a mood.

310
00:16:56,180 --> 00:16:58,150
Li Wu Si, think for yourself.

311
00:16:58,670 --> 00:17:01,390
Since you have your girl,
who have you kept in your mind?

312
00:17:03,150 --> 00:17:04,030
You're always like this...

313
00:17:04,230 --> 00:17:06,020
Has Tong Tong eaten yet?

314
00:17:06,109 --> 00:17:07,660
Did Tong Tong drink any water?

315
00:17:07,750 --> 00:17:09,260
Where did Tong Tong go?

316
00:17:09,349 --> 00:17:10,990
Has Tong Tong come back yet?

317
00:17:11,990 --> 00:17:14,069
You talk about her all the time.

318
00:17:14,589 --> 00:17:16,150
I didn't say much about you before.

319
00:17:16,470 --> 00:17:17,349
But now,

320
00:17:17,589 --> 00:17:18,670
she has gone to school.

321
00:17:19,150 --> 00:17:20,670
What are you doing all day long?

322
00:17:21,030 --> 00:17:22,420
You don't think about anything else.

323
00:17:22,510 --> 00:17:23,859
What do you mean?

324
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:25,760
Only your girl was given a life?

325
00:17:25,869 --> 00:17:26,950
And me? None.

326
00:17:27,109 --> 00:17:28,140
-No.
-Yes or no?

327
00:17:28,230 --> 00:17:29,910
-No, no.
-I am an extra.

328
00:17:30,030 --> 00:17:31,140
No, no.

329
00:17:31,230 --> 00:17:32,740
Why are you jealous of her?

330
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:34,420
-Let me rub your legs.
-No, no need.

331
00:17:34,520 --> 00:17:35,400
I don't need you.

332
00:17:35,490 --> 00:17:36,370
You're saying I'm jealous.

333
00:17:36,910 --> 00:17:37,870
Look at yourself,

334
00:17:38,910 --> 00:17:39,790
do you deserve it?

335
00:17:40,590 --> 00:17:41,710
You are angry, right?

336
00:17:42,710 --> 00:17:43,590
How about this...

337
00:17:44,070 --> 00:17:45,580
Our girl has grown up,

338
00:17:45,990 --> 00:17:47,390
she can do whatever she wants.

339
00:17:48,030 --> 00:17:50,780
Okay?
Then let's just enjoy our time together.

340
00:17:50,860 --> 00:17:51,830
Is that okay?

341
00:17:52,470 --> 00:17:53,500
Is that okay?

342
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:54,470
Of course not.

343
00:17:54,590 --> 00:17:55,590
You can't bear it.

344
00:17:56,030 --> 00:17:57,430
What can't I bear?

345
00:17:57,710 --> 00:17:59,500
Our girl will have a boyfriend someday.

346
00:17:59,590 --> 00:18:00,710
Her boyfriend will take care of her.

347
00:18:01,150 --> 00:18:03,180
I think there's only one thing
I need to do now.

348
00:18:04,030 --> 00:18:05,630
What is it?

349
00:18:06,830 --> 00:18:08,070
That is...

350
00:18:08,550 --> 00:18:10,110
to grow old with you.

351
00:18:37,230 --> 00:18:39,300
I heard there's a very handsome boy
in the philosophy department.

352
00:18:39,380 --> 00:18:40,510
Let's go and see.

353
00:18:40,790 --> 00:18:42,100
Finally, we are free!

354
00:18:42,190 --> 00:18:43,060
Let's eat, let's eat.

355
00:18:43,150 --> 00:18:44,500
What's your major?

356
00:18:44,590 --> 00:18:45,710
Preschool Education.

357
00:18:45,910 --> 00:18:46,950
Preschool Education?

358
00:18:47,190 --> 00:18:48,540
What a funny major.

359
00:18:48,620 --> 00:18:50,300
Aren't you ashamed?

360
00:18:50,380 --> 00:18:51,910
Yeah, I've never heard of it.

361
00:18:53,900 --> 00:18:55,270
Why are you guys talking like that?

362
00:18:55,470 --> 00:18:56,430
Do we know each other?

363
00:18:56,630 --> 00:18:57,900
Can't you respect me?

364
00:18:57,990 --> 00:18:59,300
No way.

365
00:18:59,700 --> 00:19:00,670
-Who are you?
-Get your hands off me.

366
00:19:00,750 --> 00:19:01,750
What's wrong with Preschool Education?

367
00:19:02,230 --> 00:19:03,110
Ouch.

368
00:19:04,030 --> 00:19:04,910
Get lost.

369
00:19:06,580 --> 00:19:08,230
Bro. You rock!

370
00:19:08,430 --> 00:19:09,860
Don't let others scold you like that.

371
00:19:10,380 --> 00:19:11,490
This being coward...

372
00:19:11,590 --> 00:19:12,940
Summon up the courage, he will give in.

373
00:19:13,030 --> 00:19:14,700
-Understand?
-We have to be smart.

374
00:19:15,110 --> 00:19:16,990
Bro. What's your major?

375
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:20,630
Preschool Education.

376
00:19:22,180 --> 00:19:24,310
Bro. What's your name?

377
00:19:25,700 --> 00:19:27,280
The military training is finally over.

378
00:19:27,630 --> 00:19:28,990
We're finally out of it.

379
00:19:30,270 --> 00:19:31,190
Time for food.

380
00:19:34,310 --> 00:19:35,230
I've finally found you.

381
00:19:36,630 --> 00:19:37,510
Xiao.

382
00:19:37,670 --> 00:19:38,550
Hello.

383
00:19:38,830 --> 00:19:39,910
What are you doing here?

384
00:19:40,910 --> 00:19:42,070
I came to see you.

385
00:19:43,270 --> 00:19:44,430
Don't you have class?

386
00:19:44,790 --> 00:19:45,750
Why did you look for me?

387
00:19:48,470 --> 00:19:49,350
I...

388
00:19:50,110 --> 00:19:50,990
I...

389
00:19:51,110 --> 00:19:52,430
What's wrong?

390
00:19:52,990 --> 00:19:55,190
Why has your attitude changed
when you got to college?

391
00:19:58,630 --> 00:19:59,510
Well...

392
00:19:59,670 --> 00:20:02,150
Aren't we done eating?
We all are. Let's go.

393
00:20:03,750 --> 00:20:04,630
We've finished.

394
00:20:11,910 --> 00:20:13,030
He is so handsome.

395
00:20:13,390 --> 00:20:14,740
What does that guy have to do with her?

396
00:20:14,830 --> 00:20:16,110
They are certainly not friends.

397
00:20:16,860 --> 00:20:18,180
I know too much about that.

398
00:20:18,830 --> 00:20:20,380
Stop gossiping. Let's go.

399
00:20:20,470 --> 00:20:21,460
Did you eat?

400
00:20:21,550 --> 00:20:22,430
No.

401
00:20:25,150 --> 00:20:26,100
Here you are.

402
00:20:26,190 --> 00:20:27,950
I haven't tried it yet. You go ahead.

403
00:20:29,910 --> 00:20:30,790
It's not easy.

404
00:20:31,550 --> 00:20:33,860
I shall live to see you treat me to lunch.

405
00:20:33,950 --> 00:20:35,460
Isn't that sandwich for you?

406
00:20:35,830 --> 00:20:37,750
I'm just kidding. Why are you angry?

407
00:20:38,590 --> 00:20:40,630
Eat quickly then go back to school.

408
00:20:42,710 --> 00:20:44,630
Won't you show me around your school?

409
00:20:44,870 --> 00:20:46,230
What's there to see?

410
00:20:46,460 --> 00:20:47,500
Go back to class after lunch.

411
00:20:47,590 --> 00:20:49,590
There aren't that many courser
at the beginning of the semester,

412
00:20:50,030 --> 00:20:51,790
and our schools
aren't far from each other.

413
00:20:52,150 --> 00:20:53,390
As long as there is no class,

414
00:20:53,670 --> 00:20:54,950
I can come to you.

415
00:20:55,670 --> 00:20:57,630
[We all need to know where we come from]

416
00:20:58,510 --> 00:20:59,990
[and where we are going back to.]

417
00:21:01,630 --> 00:21:02,510
Duan Xiao.

418
00:21:03,230 --> 00:21:04,870
You should study hard.

419
00:21:05,310 --> 00:21:06,870
We're both in college now.

420
00:21:07,110 --> 00:21:08,300
We should have new friends

421
00:21:08,390 --> 00:21:09,870
and new lives.

422
00:21:10,630 --> 00:21:12,670
Please stop coming to our school
all the time.

423
00:21:14,190 --> 00:21:15,950
What are you talking about?

424
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:18,540
New life and new friends?

425
00:21:18,630 --> 00:21:19,550
I don't need that.

426
00:21:19,790 --> 00:21:21,670
It's enough for me to stay with you.

427
00:21:22,470 --> 00:21:24,270
I don't care about anyone else.

428
00:21:28,790 --> 00:21:29,910
Well, you go ahead.

429
00:21:30,390 --> 00:21:31,590
I'm going to look for them.

430
00:21:35,830 --> 00:21:37,910
Be careful on your way back.

431
00:21:49,230 --> 00:21:50,190
What are you doing here?

432
00:21:51,150 --> 00:21:52,220
Let's have a drink.

433
00:21:52,310 --> 00:21:54,510
What... What are you doing here?

434
00:21:54,710 --> 00:21:55,590
I'll tell you later.

435
00:21:57,430 --> 00:21:58,340
You are so amazing.

436
00:21:58,420 --> 00:22:00,790
You are chasing Li Jin Bu all the way.

437
00:22:01,310 --> 00:22:02,190
You are so amazing too.

438
00:22:02,470 --> 00:22:04,940
Aren't you chasing Li Qing Tong
all the way?

439
00:22:05,020 --> 00:22:06,030
I'm not.

440
00:22:09,510 --> 00:22:10,550
Do you think I believe it?

441
00:22:11,180 --> 00:22:12,060
Believe it or not.

442
00:22:12,430 --> 00:22:13,630
You're just too stubborn.

443
00:22:13,990 --> 00:22:15,140
You don't have the guts to see her.

444
00:22:16,110 --> 00:22:17,230
I don't have the guts for what?

445
00:22:17,750 --> 00:22:18,870
Didn't I go on the graduation trip?

446
00:22:19,230 --> 00:22:20,180
Haven't I come to her college?

447
00:22:20,270 --> 00:22:21,220
I'm right here.

448
00:22:21,300 --> 00:22:22,260
What am I afraid of?

449
00:22:22,350 --> 00:22:24,260
Yeah, you're standing
right in front of me.

450
00:22:24,350 --> 00:22:25,740
If you had the courage,
you'd stand in front of Li Qing Tong,

451
00:22:25,830 --> 00:22:26,980
and tell her you're here.

452
00:22:27,070 --> 00:22:28,980
Of course.
I'm going to see her tomorrow.

453
00:22:29,070 --> 00:22:30,540
I will say, I, Chen Jun He, am here.

454
00:22:30,910 --> 00:22:31,820
That's right.

455
00:22:31,910 --> 00:22:33,940
A man should be brave. I support you.

456
00:22:34,030 --> 00:22:34,910
Cheers.

457
00:22:42,100 --> 00:22:43,110
Will you send me back to school?

458
00:22:44,270 --> 00:22:45,310
Get lost.

459
00:22:48,670 --> 00:22:49,550
Well...

460
00:22:50,230 --> 00:22:51,190
It's nice...

461
00:22:51,990 --> 00:22:52,870
to have you here.

462
00:22:54,510 --> 00:22:56,350
Then why don't you and I work together?

463
00:22:57,470 --> 00:22:58,350
Sure.

464
00:23:02,490 --> 00:23:04,720
[Classroom Building]

465
00:23:12,350 --> 00:23:13,340
Where are you from?

466
00:23:13,630 --> 00:23:14,710
I'm from Heilongjiang.

467
00:23:15,030 --> 00:23:16,130
-What about you?
-I'm from Guangdong.

468
00:23:16,230 --> 00:23:17,150
Do me a favour after class.

469
00:23:19,110 --> 00:23:21,300
-Are you two in the same dorm?
-Yeah.

470
00:23:21,390 --> 00:23:23,310
Why does he never talk to us?

471
00:23:23,630 --> 00:23:25,710
He doesn't like to deal with girls.

472
00:23:30,230 --> 00:23:31,110
Bro.

473
00:23:31,430 --> 00:23:32,790
I've got the schedule for you.

474
00:23:35,630 --> 00:23:36,830
Well done.

475
00:23:38,690 --> 00:23:39,110
[Information on Class 2 Schedule]

476
00:23:39,110 --> 00:23:40,670
Who is Li Qing Tong?

477
00:23:42,750 --> 00:23:44,830
Don't ask questions you shouldn't ask.

478
00:23:47,310 --> 00:23:49,510
There must be something going on
between you two.

479
00:24:15,590 --> 00:24:16,470
Oops!

480
00:24:22,550 --> 00:24:23,430
Hi!

481
00:24:27,790 --> 00:24:28,790
What are you doing here?

482
00:24:29,110 --> 00:24:30,140
I'm here for class.

483
00:24:31,020 --> 00:24:33,590
But, what are you doing in our school?

484
00:24:35,710 --> 00:24:37,060
This is my school, too.

485
00:24:37,150 --> 00:24:38,100
What a coincidence!

486
00:24:38,190 --> 00:24:39,550
We were admitted to the same college.

487
00:24:45,100 --> 00:24:46,630
Calm down, class.

488
00:24:46,910 --> 00:24:48,150
Now let's get started.

489
00:24:55,990 --> 00:24:57,620
"Students of the Imperial College
in the Han Dynasty

490
00:24:57,710 --> 00:25:00,670
were called doctoral disciples or
disciples in the Western Han Dynasty."

491
00:25:01,430 --> 00:25:03,610
"In the Eastern Han Dynasty
the short form was Scarlet Students

492
00:25:03,690 --> 00:25:04,990
or Imperial College Students."

493
00:25:10,630 --> 00:25:11,950
"In the Han Dynasty, there is no..."

494
00:25:19,170 --> 00:25:20,110
Guys,

495
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:22,140
let's call it a day.

496
00:25:22,620 --> 00:25:23,670
Before the class is over,

497
00:25:23,940 --> 00:25:25,260
I'd like to ask a student

498
00:25:25,350 --> 00:25:27,790
to talk about their feelings
about this class.

499
00:25:29,220 --> 00:25:30,380
The boy in the jeans

500
00:25:30,470 --> 00:25:32,320
in the third row,

501
00:25:32,830 --> 00:25:33,710
please.

502
00:25:37,430 --> 00:25:38,390
Yes, it's you.

503
00:25:45,710 --> 00:25:46,910
I feel good,

504
00:25:47,430 --> 00:25:48,350
very good.

505
00:25:49,030 --> 00:25:49,990
Which class are you in?

506
00:25:50,870 --> 00:25:51,750
Class One.

507
00:25:51,990 --> 00:25:52,870
Which Class One is it?

508
00:25:54,910 --> 00:25:56,110
Preschool Education Class One.

509
00:25:59,150 --> 00:26:01,710
I don't think Preschool Education students
should be in my class.

510
00:26:03,750 --> 00:26:04,860
I'm interested in it,

511
00:26:04,950 --> 00:26:06,230
so I came to listen to it.

512
00:26:07,590 --> 00:26:09,020
I advise you

513
00:26:09,130 --> 00:26:10,980
to listen carefully,

514
00:26:11,070 --> 00:26:13,390
don't always stare
at the girl in front of you.

515
00:26:13,670 --> 00:26:14,700
You should

516
00:26:14,790 --> 00:26:15,820
look at me more,

517
00:26:15,910 --> 00:26:16,880
okay?

518
00:26:21,430 --> 00:26:22,790
All right, just kidding.

519
00:26:22,990 --> 00:26:23,950
Class is over.

520
00:26:34,790 --> 00:26:35,670
Chen Jun He.

521
00:26:37,430 --> 00:26:38,310
What?

522
00:26:39,030 --> 00:26:41,030
What are you doing here?

523
00:26:42,190 --> 00:26:43,630
I'm here for class.

524
00:26:43,710 --> 00:26:45,100
What the hell are you doing?

525
00:26:45,190 --> 00:26:47,670
How come you and I
are in the same school again?

526
00:26:48,310 --> 00:26:50,230
I've already told you,

527
00:26:51,350 --> 00:26:52,230
destiny.

528
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:01,870
It's called...

529
00:27:02,420 --> 00:27:03,300
destiny.

530
00:27:03,790 --> 00:27:05,150
An English noun, I've just learned it.

531
00:27:13,270 --> 00:27:14,870
Will you sit there next time?

532
00:27:17,470 --> 00:27:21,830
[No. 1 Students' Dormitory]

533
00:27:22,830 --> 00:27:24,070
I see,

534
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:26,900
I definitely had hatred against him
in my past life.

535
00:27:26,990 --> 00:27:28,540
Not only in your last life,

536
00:27:28,630 --> 00:27:29,540
but in this life too.

537
00:27:29,630 --> 00:27:30,750
It cannot be avoided.

538
00:27:31,010 --> 00:27:31,890
Li Qing Tong.

539
00:27:31,990 --> 00:27:33,500
What's your attitude towards him anyway?

540
00:27:33,590 --> 00:27:34,500
It bothers me!

541
00:27:34,590 --> 00:27:35,830
I hate it!

542
00:27:36,070 --> 00:27:37,030
I'll sum it up for her.

543
00:27:37,510 --> 00:27:39,300
She is bored, disgusted,

544
00:27:39,380 --> 00:27:40,260
and helpless.

545
00:27:40,750 --> 00:27:42,270
But he's obviously chasing you.

546
00:27:42,590 --> 00:27:43,470
Chasing me?

547
00:27:44,960 --> 00:27:45,840
Oh no.

548
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:47,860
You know what he did to me
for three years in high school?

549
00:27:48,350 --> 00:27:50,870
He almost kicked me out of high school
all three years.

550
00:27:51,550 --> 00:27:53,430
You don't know what I looked like
in high school.

551
00:27:53,990 --> 00:27:54,950
I fought.

552
00:27:55,040 --> 00:27:55,920
What else?

553
00:27:56,030 --> 00:27:58,580
I instigated the elder boys
to do bad things for me.

554
00:27:58,670 --> 00:27:59,470
And I...

555
00:27:59,570 --> 00:28:01,640
I paid social men to cheat the school.

556
00:28:01,710 --> 00:28:03,460
If I were the principal,
I'd have fired myself.

557
00:28:03,550 --> 00:28:04,430
Wow!

558
00:28:04,630 --> 00:28:06,670
You have such a spectacular story?

559
00:28:07,440 --> 00:28:08,680
It was just a misunderstanding.

560
00:28:08,790 --> 00:28:10,110
What did it have to do with us?

561
00:28:10,390 --> 00:28:11,900
It's Chen Jun He who looked for troubles.

562
00:28:11,990 --> 00:28:12,870
Exactly.

563
00:28:14,260 --> 00:28:16,350
But I can tell from his eyes,

564
00:28:16,950 --> 00:28:18,390
he absolutely likes you.

565
00:28:20,190 --> 00:28:21,070
That's true.

566
00:28:21,710 --> 00:28:23,630
I've seen a hundred romantic movies.

567
00:28:23,710 --> 00:28:25,070
Whether a person likes someone or not,

568
00:28:25,150 --> 00:28:26,350
I can tell at a glance.

569
00:28:27,150 --> 00:28:28,300
He is this kind of person

570
00:28:28,390 --> 00:28:30,540
who would bully the girl he likes,

571
00:28:30,630 --> 00:28:32,310
trying to get her attention.

572
00:28:32,950 --> 00:28:33,910
The way is...

573
00:28:34,350 --> 00:28:35,500
stupid and annoying.

574
00:28:36,110 --> 00:28:38,140
But that's how he expresses his feeling.

575
00:28:38,230 --> 00:28:39,110
Anyway,

576
00:28:39,460 --> 00:28:41,220
why are they so stupid?

577
00:28:44,300 --> 00:28:45,180
Whatever.

578
00:28:46,110 --> 00:28:47,710
What does it matter to me
whether he likes me or not?

579
00:28:48,510 --> 00:28:50,020
I don't want anything to do with him.

580
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:52,750
My life is not so hard, I'm afraid I'll
be bullied to death by him someday.

581
00:28:53,980 --> 00:28:56,140
It's really hard to satisfy you.

582
00:28:56,230 --> 00:28:58,540
Such handsome men chasing you,
and you both disagree?

583
00:28:58,630 --> 00:28:59,870
It's unfair.

584
00:29:30,180 --> 00:29:31,060
Xiao.

585
00:29:33,700 --> 00:29:34,420
Here you are.

586
00:29:34,510 --> 00:29:35,430
Fruit for you.

587
00:29:35,670 --> 00:29:36,550
Thanks.

588
00:29:36,910 --> 00:29:38,310
Fruit is quite expensive these days.

589
00:29:38,670 --> 00:29:39,550
Strawberries.

590
00:29:48,380 --> 00:29:49,260
Well...

591
00:29:49,470 --> 00:29:51,270
Let's go to the canteen to eat fruit.

592
00:29:51,910 --> 00:29:53,350
Let's go. Hurry up.

593
00:29:56,110 --> 00:29:56,990
What's wrong with you?

594
00:29:58,230 --> 00:29:59,110
Nothing.

595
00:29:59,470 --> 00:30:00,750
Then why are you doing like this?

596
00:30:02,790 --> 00:30:06,220
I just think
we should keep a little distance.

597
00:30:06,310 --> 00:30:08,350
Give me some time to think it over.

598
00:30:08,830 --> 00:30:11,070
Even if I explain it to you now,
you won't understand.

599
00:30:12,270 --> 00:30:13,590
So give me some time,

600
00:30:13,860 --> 00:30:14,740
okay?

601
00:30:17,950 --> 00:30:18,830
Okay.

602
00:30:18,990 --> 00:30:19,870
It's up to you.

603
00:30:20,900 --> 00:30:21,780
It's so cold outside,

604
00:30:21,870 --> 00:30:23,470
you'd better hurry back to school.

605
00:30:33,790 --> 00:30:35,510
Hua, look at yourself.

606
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:39,140
He sent you so much fruit all the way,

607
00:30:39,230 --> 00:30:41,260
and you didn't even touch it.

608
00:30:42,230 --> 00:30:44,550
You can't be satisfied
with someone concerned about you.

609
00:30:45,110 --> 00:30:46,980
I want someone concerned about me,
but there isn't.

610
00:30:47,710 --> 00:30:49,110
There's someone concerned about you.

611
00:30:49,430 --> 00:30:51,510
Chen Jun He is concerned
about you, isn't he?

612
00:30:52,260 --> 00:30:54,740
She doesn't want Chen Jun He
to be concerned about her,

613
00:30:54,830 --> 00:30:57,230
she prefers Wu Zhi Xun.

614
00:30:58,150 --> 00:30:59,150
Who is Wu Zhi Xun?

615
00:31:00,150 --> 00:31:01,310
Is he handsome?

616
00:31:01,390 --> 00:31:03,790
This is a little more complicated.

617
00:31:04,600 --> 00:31:05,590
It doesn't matter.

618
00:31:05,670 --> 00:31:08,070
We're all apart anyway.

619
00:31:12,230 --> 00:31:13,950
If you don't eat the fruit,
shall we split it up?

620
00:31:14,590 --> 00:31:15,500
You go ahead.

621
00:31:15,580 --> 00:31:16,460
I'm going to sleep.

622
00:31:17,710 --> 00:31:18,590
Good night.

623
00:31:50,670 --> 00:31:51,630
Hello?

624
00:31:52,260 --> 00:31:53,230
Auntie

625
00:31:53,310 --> 00:31:54,940
I was a classmate of Wu Zhi Xun.

626
00:31:55,030 --> 00:31:56,180
I just called to ask if he's...

627
00:31:58,590 --> 00:31:59,470
Then...

628
00:32:00,270 --> 00:32:01,150
[Who called?]

629
00:32:01,590 --> 00:32:03,310
Was it Li Qing Tong again?

630
00:32:04,030 --> 00:32:05,380
All right, keep your voice down.

631
00:32:05,470 --> 00:32:06,870
Has she been calling a lot lately?

632
00:32:08,590 --> 00:32:10,070
[She calls every few days.]

633
00:32:10,710 --> 00:32:12,830
[Previously she came to our house.]

634
00:32:14,510 --> 00:32:16,150
[The girl is quite persistent.]

635
00:32:17,310 --> 00:32:20,580
The current situation of our son
is all because of her.

636
00:32:20,670 --> 00:32:22,470
All right, stop it.

637
00:32:27,070 --> 00:32:27,950
Mum.

638
00:32:28,550 --> 00:32:29,740
I'm going to resume
my interrupted studies.

639
00:32:44,310 --> 00:32:45,190
Li Qing Tong.

640
00:32:47,340 --> 00:32:48,590
What are you doing here again?

641
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:50,110
Here, give this pair of gloves to her.

642
00:32:50,630 --> 00:32:52,190
Why don't you give it to her yourself?

643
00:32:52,670 --> 00:32:54,270
She told me to keep a distance from her.

644
00:32:54,470 --> 00:32:55,660
I don't know why.

645
00:32:55,750 --> 00:32:56,870
Anyway, please give it to her for me.

646
00:32:58,430 --> 00:32:59,590
That's the way she is.

647
00:32:59,670 --> 00:33:00,870
-Don't worry.
-She'll be all right in a couple of days.

648
00:33:01,390 --> 00:33:02,270
I know.

649
00:33:02,510 --> 00:33:03,630
I know her.

650
00:33:05,220 --> 00:33:06,140
Remember,

651
00:33:06,230 --> 00:33:07,550
don't say I gave it to her.

652
00:33:08,110 --> 00:33:09,460
Any other excuse is fine.

653
00:33:10,070 --> 00:33:10,950
I'm leaving.

654
00:33:15,790 --> 00:33:17,270
No one bought it for me.

655
00:33:21,470 --> 00:33:22,350
Oh, you're back.

656
00:33:30,390 --> 00:33:31,270
What is this?

657
00:33:32,800 --> 00:33:34,390
I met Duan Xiao downstairs.

658
00:33:34,910 --> 00:33:35,940
It was so cold that

659
00:33:36,030 --> 00:33:37,630
he bought you gloves.

660
00:33:39,270 --> 00:33:40,630
And he told me not to tell you.

661
00:33:43,270 --> 00:33:44,590
To tell you the truth,

662
00:33:44,910 --> 00:33:46,430
Duan Xiao is very nice to you.

663
00:33:46,910 --> 00:33:49,470
What's wrong with you?
Why are you ignoring him in college?

664
00:33:49,830 --> 00:33:52,870
We should have our own lives
now that we're in college.

665
00:33:53,470 --> 00:33:54,500
But in college,

666
00:33:54,590 --> 00:33:56,470
we can also be in a relationship.

667
00:33:58,140 --> 00:33:59,140
Duan Xiao is very nice.

668
00:33:59,230 --> 00:34:00,820
You should take him
into serious consideration.

669
00:34:00,910 --> 00:34:02,300
Then why aren't you in love?

670
00:34:02,380 --> 00:34:03,750
Who am I going to date?

671
00:34:04,140 --> 00:34:06,190
Are you still thinking about Wu Zhi Xun?

672
00:34:09,230 --> 00:34:10,190
Go and watch your turtle.

673
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:31,530
[Pipi Lu Collection]

674
00:34:33,389 --> 00:34:34,590
[Tomorrow is
the college entrance examination.]

675
00:34:35,110 --> 00:34:36,750
[You're still thinking
about meeting that girl?]

676
00:34:36,989 --> 00:34:40,420
[Wu Zhi Xun,
are you trying to piss me off?]

677
00:34:40,510 --> 00:34:41,830
[Why don't you let me see her?]

678
00:34:42,150 --> 00:34:44,030
[You asked me not to go to school.
I've obeyed.]

679
00:34:44,350 --> 00:34:45,699
[Now we have
the college entrance examination.]

680
00:34:45,790 --> 00:34:48,420
[I just want to see her once and encourage
her to take a good exam, can't I?]

681
00:34:48,510 --> 00:34:50,790
[What you need right now
is to take care of yourself.]

682
00:34:51,389 --> 00:34:52,980
[Look at you now,]

683
00:34:53,070 --> 00:34:54,500
[can you get into your ideal university?]

684
00:34:54,590 --> 00:34:56,670
[-I don't care.]
[-Say it again!]

685
00:34:57,590 --> 00:34:59,790
[I... do not care!]

686
00:34:59,790 --> 00:35:00,550
[Pipi Lu Collection]

687
00:35:03,550 --> 00:35:04,630
[You don't care?]

688
00:35:06,750 --> 00:35:07,670
[You don't care.]

689
00:35:08,230 --> 00:35:09,430
[You don't care.]

690
00:35:12,350 --> 00:35:14,630
[I'll see whether you care or not.]

691
00:35:16,230 --> 00:35:17,790
[You're not allowed to go anywhere today.]

692
00:35:18,270 --> 00:35:19,710
[Anywhere!]

693
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:27,100
I'm really worried about him

694
00:35:27,670 --> 00:35:29,110
being out by himself.

695
00:35:29,510 --> 00:35:30,510
Let him go.

696
00:35:31,310 --> 00:35:33,150
He doesn't want to stay
in this house anyway.

697
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:35,570
As long as he is willing to resume
his interrupted studies,

698
00:35:35,570 --> 00:35:35,830
[Pipi Lu Collection]

699
00:35:35,830 --> 00:35:37,190
I will agree to anything.

700
00:35:40,990 --> 00:35:43,430
[No.2 Dining Hall]

701
00:35:43,470 --> 00:35:45,750
You should learn to judge her emotions.

702
00:35:46,070 --> 00:35:48,940
She's tired of looking at you now,
so don't always stick to her.

703
00:35:49,030 --> 00:35:50,580
Keep your distance, understand?

704
00:35:50,670 --> 00:35:51,790
Why don't you keep your distance?

705
00:35:52,510 --> 00:35:54,310
Am I not keeping my distance now?

706
00:35:55,110 --> 00:35:56,190
Are you doing it voluntarily?

707
00:35:57,230 --> 00:35:59,510
-Can't you...
-All right, let's eat.

708
00:36:06,790 --> 00:36:07,670
Buddy,

709
00:36:08,140 --> 00:36:09,590
we just had a roll call,

710
00:36:09,990 --> 00:36:11,630
and the instructor asked you
to go to the office.

711
00:36:12,830 --> 00:36:14,630
Didn't I ask you to answer for me?

712
00:36:15,620 --> 00:36:17,030
How could I answer that?

713
00:36:17,590 --> 00:36:19,190
You and I are the only boys in our class.

714
00:36:19,550 --> 00:36:20,950
Teachers aren't blind.

715
00:36:21,550 --> 00:36:22,590
Okay, I got it.

716
00:36:24,070 --> 00:36:27,350
By the way,
a few more girls asked me about you today.

717
00:36:29,070 --> 00:36:30,230
He cares about no one

718
00:36:30,670 --> 00:36:31,910
but Li Qing Tong.

719
00:36:33,030 --> 00:36:34,030
Do you want to be beaten again?

720
00:36:34,510 --> 00:36:35,390
Look,

721
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,380
so stubborn.

722
00:36:36,470 --> 00:36:37,740
Still don't admit it?

723
00:36:38,130 --> 00:36:39,060
Chasing girls?

724
00:36:39,150 --> 00:36:40,710
I'm the one.

725
00:36:41,590 --> 00:36:42,550
What do you know?

726
00:36:43,550 --> 00:36:45,310
What do you mean?

727
00:36:45,660 --> 00:36:47,260
I know girls' mind best.

728
00:36:47,350 --> 00:36:48,740
It'll work out for you in minutes.

729
00:36:51,670 --> 00:36:53,470
It's been a long time
since school started.

730
00:36:53,710 --> 00:36:55,230
How come no boys chase me?

731
00:36:56,390 --> 00:36:58,230
Are they all blind?

732
00:36:58,390 --> 00:36:59,550
It's only been a few days
since school started.

733
00:36:59,630 --> 00:37:01,060
Be normal, please.

734
00:37:01,310 --> 00:37:02,990
You're not normal.

735
00:37:03,430 --> 00:37:05,860
Except for going to class,
you just eat and sleep every day.

736
00:37:05,950 --> 00:37:07,030
Can't you be a little bit more ambitious?

737
00:37:07,510 --> 00:37:09,420
Isn't love important?

738
00:37:11,450 --> 00:37:12,380
Jin Bu,

739
00:37:12,470 --> 00:37:13,870
how are you getting along with that boy?

740
00:37:14,280 --> 00:37:15,540
He's not my boyfriend.

741
00:37:15,630 --> 00:37:17,270
I've told you I'm not in a relationship.

742
00:37:17,350 --> 00:37:19,420
But he definitely likes you, right?

743
00:37:19,510 --> 00:37:21,070
So what if he likes me?

744
00:37:21,550 --> 00:37:22,820
We can't be together.

745
00:37:22,910 --> 00:37:23,870
Why?

746
00:37:25,150 --> 00:37:26,910
You really don't like him at all?

747
00:37:30,270 --> 00:37:31,790
Don't kid yourself.

748
00:37:33,910 --> 00:37:34,790
Think back...

749
00:37:35,470 --> 00:37:38,030
Ever since you met him that day,

750
00:37:38,580 --> 00:37:41,790
you've been morose and distracted.

751
00:37:42,350 --> 00:37:43,230
Why?

752
00:37:43,510 --> 00:37:45,020
Is it because canteen food tastes bad?

753
00:37:45,110 --> 00:37:46,390
It does taste bad.

754
00:37:47,820 --> 00:37:49,630
We were just getting down to business,
don't be troublesome.

755
00:37:50,750 --> 00:37:51,630
Sweetheart.

756
00:37:51,950 --> 00:37:52,830
Think about it.

757
00:37:53,030 --> 00:37:55,070
If you didn't like him at all,

758
00:37:55,350 --> 00:37:57,960
it wouldn't mess up your mind.

759
00:37:59,030 --> 00:38:00,660
You are like this now
because you like him.

760
00:38:00,750 --> 00:38:01,630
It must be true.

761
00:38:02,510 --> 00:38:03,820
You are really nosy.

762
00:38:03,910 --> 00:38:05,380
Why do you meddle in her relationship?

763
00:38:05,470 --> 00:38:06,470
You don't understand.

764
00:38:06,790 --> 00:38:08,620
I was pointing her in the right direction

765
00:38:08,910 --> 00:38:11,430
to save a good boy.

766
00:38:11,700 --> 00:38:12,950
Otherwise,
it will be too late to regret later.

767
00:38:15,110 --> 00:38:15,990
Where is Li Qing Tong?

768
00:38:16,790 --> 00:38:18,300
I'll teach her a lesson
when she comes back.

769
00:38:20,190 --> 00:38:21,710
What do girls need most?

770
00:38:24,390 --> 00:38:26,660
They need you to treat them
like the apple of your eye.

771
00:38:26,950 --> 00:38:28,910
And prove your affection to the world.

772
00:38:29,350 --> 00:38:30,230
Right?

773
00:38:31,550 --> 00:38:33,990
But, isn't that a shame?

774
00:38:34,270 --> 00:38:36,340
Yeah, we're just freshmen.

775
00:38:36,670 --> 00:38:39,310
It won't be so good for us
to chase girls so blatantly.

776
00:38:40,350 --> 00:38:41,710
Then there's nothing I can do.

777
00:38:42,510 --> 00:38:43,910
Just keep your distance,

778
00:38:44,710 --> 00:38:46,990
and wait until your junior
and senior years.

779
00:38:47,350 --> 00:38:49,950
They'll all have boyfriends by then.

780
00:38:50,790 --> 00:38:51,670
You two

781
00:38:52,470 --> 00:38:53,350
will have no chance.

782
00:38:53,950 --> 00:38:56,460
But, we can't be too direct, right?

783
00:38:56,550 --> 00:38:58,070
What should we say then?

784
00:38:58,550 --> 00:38:59,700
Just ask them out.

785
00:38:59,780 --> 00:39:01,580
If you don't have the guts,
then go out together.

786
00:39:01,670 --> 00:39:02,550
Two versus two.

787
00:39:02,630 --> 00:39:03,780
You guys can also help each other.

788
00:39:03,870 --> 00:39:05,310
I do have the guts,

789
00:39:05,390 --> 00:39:06,990
I used to date Hua alone.

790
00:39:09,070 --> 00:39:10,340
I prefer two versus two.

791
00:39:11,110 --> 00:39:13,700
Whenever I go out alone with Li Qing Tong,
it never ends well.

792
00:39:13,790 --> 00:39:14,670
So what are you waiting for?

793
00:39:14,910 --> 00:39:15,790
Have a date!

794
00:39:20,870 --> 00:39:22,220
Aren't you good at romance?

795
00:39:22,630 --> 00:39:23,560
Help us then.

796
00:39:25,110 --> 00:39:26,550
Li Qing Tong.

797
00:39:26,870 --> 00:39:28,380
Li Jin Bu.

798
00:39:28,470 --> 00:39:29,790
Speak louder.

799
00:39:30,670 --> 00:39:32,710
How can you treat your teacher like this?

800
00:39:34,710 --> 00:39:36,150
Li Qing Tong.

801
00:39:36,590 --> 00:39:38,180
Li Jin Bu.

802
00:39:39,470 --> 00:39:41,670
How can you have followers
wherever you go?

803
00:39:43,110 --> 00:39:44,220
This is the fate of a leader.

804
00:39:44,310 --> 00:39:45,510
Understand?

805
00:39:46,630 --> 00:39:48,110
Speak louder.
I can't even hear it from here.

806
00:39:48,190 --> 00:39:49,110
Can they hear it?

807
00:39:52,230 --> 00:39:53,740
Li Jin Bu.

808
00:39:53,830 --> 00:39:55,100
Li Qing Tong.

809
00:39:55,190 --> 00:39:56,950
Come out for dinner!

810
00:39:57,430 --> 00:39:58,310
Who is it?

811
00:39:58,470 --> 00:39:59,700
Who are you?

812
00:39:59,790 --> 00:40:01,910
Are you Li Jin Bu or Li Qing Tong?

813
00:40:02,350 --> 00:40:04,070
Shout out of the way.

814
00:40:06,710 --> 00:40:08,390
That's not her. Keep shouting!

815
00:40:09,830 --> 00:40:11,140
Li Jin Bu.

816
00:40:11,230 --> 00:40:12,590
Li Qing Tong.

817
00:40:14,310 --> 00:40:15,100
What are you shouting about?

818
00:40:15,190 --> 00:40:16,990
Who are you? Are you nuts?

819
00:40:17,990 --> 00:40:19,310
He asked me to.

820
00:40:23,830 --> 00:40:26,230
Chen Jun He, are you crazy?

821
00:40:26,870 --> 00:40:27,940
You are crazy.

822
00:40:28,020 --> 00:40:29,820
-Come down to scold if you can.
-I...

823
00:40:29,910 --> 00:40:30,870
You just wait and see.

824
00:40:35,470 --> 00:40:36,350
It's still up to me.

825
00:40:36,670 --> 00:40:37,830
Make an appointment in a sentence.

826
00:40:38,070 --> 00:40:39,150
What should I do?

827
00:40:40,430 --> 00:40:41,310
You find the way.

828
00:40:43,940 --> 00:40:44,820
Keep shouting.

829
00:40:44,910 --> 00:40:45,790
Why did you stop shouting?

830
00:40:47,310 --> 00:40:48,460
Because I've seen you,

831
00:40:48,550 --> 00:40:49,510
there is no need to shout.

832
00:40:57,230 --> 00:40:59,150
The one who shouted with you...

833
00:40:59,430 --> 00:41:00,590
Why didn't he come?

834
00:41:00,910 --> 00:41:02,870
He said he wasn't hungry,
so he went back to school.

835
00:41:03,430 --> 00:41:04,710
You are so ungrateful.

836
00:41:05,310 --> 00:41:06,340
He was so disgraceful

837
00:41:06,420 --> 00:41:07,940
shouting downstairs for you,

838
00:41:08,030 --> 00:41:09,630
but you drove him away at dinner time.

839
00:41:10,820 --> 00:41:11,700
Tell us,

840
00:41:11,990 --> 00:41:12,910
why did you call us here?

841
00:41:15,550 --> 00:41:17,390
Duan Xiao said he wanted to have dinner
with Li Jin Bu

842
00:41:17,480 --> 00:41:18,710
and asked me to be with him.

843
00:41:22,860 --> 00:41:23,740
Yes.

844
00:41:24,430 --> 00:41:25,310
Yes.

845
00:41:25,550 --> 00:41:27,790
We just wanted to have dinner
together with you

846
00:41:27,870 --> 00:41:29,070
to exchange our feelings.

847
00:41:30,390 --> 00:41:31,270
Yes.

848
00:41:33,030 --> 00:41:35,270
I've finally managed to get into college,

849
00:41:35,350 --> 00:41:37,390
and wanted to have a new life.

850
00:41:37,590 --> 00:41:40,270
Why should I exchange
my feelings with you?

851
00:41:41,510 --> 00:41:43,270
Eat it yourself if you want to, I won't.

852
00:41:43,830 --> 00:41:44,990
Why are you leaving?

853
00:41:46,310 --> 00:41:47,900
Chen Jun He.

854
00:41:47,990 --> 00:41:49,700
Don't do what you did in high school.

855
00:41:49,790 --> 00:41:51,350
You just want to annoy me every day.

856
00:41:52,290 --> 00:41:53,170
I'm speechless.

857
00:41:53,270 --> 00:41:55,750
I don't know what went wrong
with my fate.

858
00:41:56,070 --> 00:41:57,990
Why are we in the same school again?

859
00:41:59,150 --> 00:42:01,260
By the way,
why on earth did you come to our school?

860
00:42:01,350 --> 00:42:02,670
Isn't that obvious?

861
00:42:03,390 --> 00:42:04,390
You knew it again?

862
00:42:05,310 --> 00:42:06,550
Then why are you here again?

863
00:42:07,470 --> 00:42:09,020
I just wanted to ask...

864
00:42:09,410 --> 00:42:10,470
why are you

865
00:42:10,550 --> 00:42:12,190
suddenly treating me like this.

866
00:42:15,230 --> 00:42:16,590
I've already told you,

867
00:42:17,380 --> 00:42:18,630
give me some time.

868
00:42:19,750 --> 00:42:22,110
But it has been a long time.

869
00:42:29,190 --> 00:42:31,550
No...
Aren't you going to treat me to dinner?

870
00:42:32,550 --> 00:42:33,550
Let's go and buy something.

871
00:42:39,710 --> 00:42:40,590
What would you like to eat?

872
00:42:41,350 --> 00:42:42,460
Do you really want to eat?

873
00:42:42,550 --> 00:42:44,430
Didn't you see what was going on?

874
00:42:48,390 --> 00:42:49,830
What's wrong with Li Jin Bu?

875
00:42:51,230 --> 00:42:53,110
Actually, I don't know
what happened to her.

876
00:42:53,500 --> 00:42:55,940
But she's always so baffling.

877
00:42:57,390 --> 00:42:59,390
Maybe she'll be all right
in a couple of days.

878
00:43:00,870 --> 00:43:01,750
Wait a minute.

879
00:43:03,350 --> 00:43:06,550
Since we're here...
let's get something to eat. It's on me.

880
00:43:06,950 --> 00:43:08,710
Even if I wanted to,
I wouldn't eat with you.

881
00:43:09,030 --> 00:43:11,630
Can't I make some new friends
in such a big school?

882
00:43:12,270 --> 00:43:13,150
Wait.

883
00:43:13,270 --> 00:43:14,550
What new friend?

884
00:43:14,790 --> 00:43:15,740
Which department is he in?

885
00:43:15,850 --> 00:43:17,210
Why are you asking so many questions?
Don't follow me.

886
00:43:17,290 --> 00:43:18,690
Please tell me something about it.

887
00:43:19,710 --> 00:43:20,710
What happened to you?

888
00:43:21,710 --> 00:43:23,030
Did I do something wrong?

889
00:43:27,710 --> 00:43:30,030
I know I'm being unreasonable.

890
00:43:30,870 --> 00:43:32,790
We used to be good friends,

891
00:43:33,550 --> 00:43:34,950
but now I'm doing this to you.

892
00:43:37,470 --> 00:43:39,510
I don't know how to explain it to you.

893
00:43:40,950 --> 00:43:42,310
I know you're good to me.

894
00:43:44,030 --> 00:43:46,150
And I also want to continue
to go down with you.

895
00:43:46,630 --> 00:43:48,950
But there is one thing I must say,

896
00:43:49,030 --> 00:43:50,980
all this is going to go away.

897
00:43:51,070 --> 00:43:52,860
I'm a person who was destined to leave.

898
00:43:52,950 --> 00:43:54,670
What do you mean "destined to leave"?
